{"tid":1534212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬鞍山中學又黎料","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:48.000Z","uid":20584,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bada7eb6fb8085fb0bb59d4f4f58dcbfeaa6f3f9","tid":1534212,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"唔識up片 <br />\n1030-1039<br />\n馬鞍山曾壁山中學 馬鞍山聖若瑟中學 兩師互片 <br />\n<br />\n兩邊鬥大聲叫口號<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人 加油<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUOmzgF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUOmzgF.png&h=737dca10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1743cee4d2a667c5e79f6c84ea17c8f506321325","tid":1534212,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a78897ed4195f3df0c8f22d41b8df40d5cf7873","tid":1534212,"uid":69525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=bfd10448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"54b434e253eaba243b1814b5b6416807ccc7c17b","tid":1534212,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ec2cf2e0d4b9f4958a93de4284ac79f047121b","tid":1534212,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},{"pid":"5f5d8b19aecd657b4790c3456aa37dec714ac32e","tid":1534212,"uid":20584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"依邊叫完 另一邊再大聲d 之後對面又大聲過佢地 <br />\n馬鞍山世界第一"},{"pid":"97b477011a6d0036615194867692e8a55888cf70","tid":1534212,"uid":155789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"聽唔到，大聲d"},{"pid":"c5315c4c845b41110073652a68f917821987f56f","tid":1534212,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9995e17a55f2f9b793de30f8bd272d0ddaa784b","tid":1534212,"uid":148192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"話知你bank幾咩成績，只要有風骨就係好學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5184d4b14483675a11ea78de483d9dbb09321d78","tid":1534212,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:11.000Z","msg":"中間隔咗馮堯敬喎，點解唔一齊參加"},{"pid":"b0e3bf706f39ff286212b13078f7bba4bcee5d0d","tid":1534212,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5184d4b14483675a11ea78de483d9dbb09321d78","tid":1534212,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:11